text: Matthew Norris (born 18 December 1992) is a South African cricketer. He is a left-handed batsman and a left-arm orthodox bowler. He made his first class debut for Cardiff MCCU against Glamorgan on 2 April 2014. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:Cardiff MCCU cricketers
